# 🎓 UVCE College Website

A responsive multi-page college website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project focuses on creating a clean, user-friendly interface with interactive components and modern UI design.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 📌 Multi-page website (Home, Department, Gallery, Contact, etc.)
* 🎨 Interactive UI with sidebar navigation and toggle functionality
* 🖼️ Image carousel and slideshow for dynamic content display
* 📱 Fully responsive design using media queries
* ⚡ Smooth user experience with JavaScript-based interactions

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript

---

## 💡 Key Highlights

* Designed structured layouts for better usability and navigation
* Implemented DOM manipulation and event handling using JavaScript
* Built reusable UI components for consistency across pages
* Focused on responsive design for mobile and desktop compatibility

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
uvce-website/
│
├── index.html
├── department.html
├── gallery.html
├── main_style.css
├── main_script.js
├── department.css
├── gallery.css
├── image/
```

